---
import EcosystemIllustration from "./illustrations/EcosystemIllustration.astro";
---

<section id="ecosystem" class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 sm:py-32">
	<div class="atmosphere absolute inset-0 -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>
	<div class="section-shell">
		<div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[.82fr_1.18fr] lg:gap-16">
			<div class="max-w-2xl">
				<p class="eyebrow reveal">A living system</p>
				<h2 class="reveal mt-4 text-4xl text-cream sm:text-6xl">Designed to keep growing.</h2>
				<p class="reveal mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted" style="--reveal-delay: 70ms">
					Follow what Homun may become, shape the direction over time, and extend what it can do through a curated ecosystem.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 90ms">
				<EcosystemIllustration />
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-14 grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-[1.12fr_.88fr]">
			<article class="operator-panel sheen reveal flex min-h-[25rem] flex-col justify-between p-7 sm:p-9">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					<span class="eyebrow">Projects</span>
					<span class="rounded-full border border-line px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-faint">Public roadmap</span>
				</div>
				<div class="my-12 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-bg/45 p-3"><p class="metric-label">Exploring</p><p class="mt-4 text-2xl text-cream">06</p></div>
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-accent/25 bg-accent/5 p-3"><p class="metric-label text-accent-bright">Building</p><p class="mt-4 text-2xl text-cream">03</p></div>
					<div class="rounded-lg border border-line bg-bg/45 p-3"><p class="metric-label">Shipped</p><p class="mt-4 text-2xl text-cream">05</p></div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl text-cream">See the direction.<br />Help shape what comes next.</h3>
					<p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
						See what Homun is exploring, what is being built and what has shipped. Community voting and suggestions will use an optional Homun account when enabled.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
						<a href="/roadmap" class="btn btn-ghost">Browse Projects</a>
						<span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-faint">Voting &amp; suggestions · Coming later</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article class="card reveal flex min-h-[25rem] flex-col justify-between p-7 sm:p-9" style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between">
					<span class="eyebrow">Marketplace</span>
					<span class="rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/8 px-2.5 py-1 font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-accent-bright">Free</span>
				</div>
				<div class="my-10 space-y-2.5" aria-hidden="true">
					<div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-line bg-bg/45 px-4 py-3"><span class="text-sm text-cream">Presentations</span><span class="metric-label">Official</span></div>
					<div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-line bg-bg/45 px-4 py-3"><span class="text-sm text-cream">Proactivity</span><span class="metric-label">Official</span></div>
					<div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-dashed border-line px-4 py-3"><span class="text-sm text-faint">More capabilities</span><span class="metric-label">Next</span></div>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-3xl text-cream">Official Homun plugins. Free at launch.</h3>
					<p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
						Browse verified plugins, understand their permissions and add new capabilities. Account-backed downloads will arrive when the online library is enabled.
					</p>
					<div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
						<a href="/marketplace" class="btn btn-ghost">Explore Marketplace</a>
						<span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-faint">Account library · Coming later</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
